xubuntu-artwork (0.23) jaunty; urgency=low

  * usplash-theme-xubuntu.c, t_animate_step_16: Use the correct image's
    width for calculating the number of pulsating steps. Previously, this
    triggered integer, and thus buffer overflows, which caused screen
    corruption and sometimes complete corruption of the VTs. (LP: #345269)

